usiness, because the fees for management and administration are usually a percentage of the amount in the fund, and even a small percent of a billion dollars is a lot of money.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f1\fs20\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid0\langfenp1033\insrsid4005967 \hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 3:\hich\f1 \'b6\loch\f1 11\tab}}\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sl480\slmult1\widctlpar
