ton Trust to allow Hutton Group to collect trustees' fees from the same accounts it was collecting brokerage commissions from, through Hutton & Co., but that Hutton Group never made or let Hutton Trust perform the trustees' duties to earn the fees, and th
\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 a\hich\af1\dbch\af13\loch\f1 
t violated the RICO statute.  I said that they hired me and the other employees by making us think Hutton Trust was a legitimate company when it wasn't, and that was fraud on us in furtherance of their RICO conspiracy against the trust clients, and firing
